{
  "texts": [
    "Clinical data is used to assess Task 2.",
    "The MICCAI-2012 dataset (Landman and Warfield, 2012) includes 134 manually segmented structures from 35 T1w MRI volumes received from Scotts Valley, California-based Neuro-Metrics, Inc.",
    "The segmentation of tissue, tumors, and structures is its principal application.",
    "In 2012, this dataset began with 80 authentic and artificial examples.",
    "The amount of training and testing data has grown over time."
  ]
}